害。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "157 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/581315092"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iq8PLwY7Qx5V4EAMaCDkxNDYyODAzILLY3Z4GMAY4fUAMcgk1ODEzMTUwOTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1675105615.7148864", "card_id": "Q_581319662", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 179}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "全国各省离婚人数排名出炉，有 10 个省份离婚登记超过 10 万对，如何看待此事？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "全国各省离婚人数排名：河南位居第一。 图源中华网"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "151 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/581319662"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq8PLwY7Qx5V4EAMaCDkxNDYzODEwIOTp3Z4GMAg4jgNADXIJNTgxMzE5NjYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1675105615.7152975", "card_id": "Q_581359988", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待中核集团发文力挺流浪地球，「你们尽管想象，我们负责实现」？科技工业的发展与科幻的关系是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "1 月 30 日晚，@中核集团发文力挺《流浪地球》：你们尽管想象，我们负责实现。 网友高呼：硬核浪漫！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-475e8d9bcec7f75869ffb2cef1aa3fd4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "145 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/581359988"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iq8PLwY7Qx5V4EAMaCDkxNDcyNzgwIPuS354GMAE4VEAOcgk1ODEzNTk5ODh4AKoBCWJpbGxib